ental, social, and governance aspects.</p><p></div></div><div id="rlta-2-does-esg-certification-make-it-easier-for-goods-to-clear-customs-in-the-eu" role="button" aria-controls="rlta-panel-2-does-esg-certification-make-it-easier-for-goods-to-clear-customs-in-the-eu" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" class="icon-faq" data-rlta-alias="2-does-esg-certification-make-it-easier-for-goods-to-clear-customs-in-the-eu" data-rlta-element="button" data-rlta-state="closed"><div data-rlta-element="heading"> 2. Does ESG certification make it easier for goods to clear customs in the EU?</div></div><div id="rlta-panel-2-does-esg-certification-make-it-easier-for-goods-to-clear-customs-in-the-eu" aria-labelledby="rlta-2-does-esg-certification-make-it-easier-for-goods-to-clear-customs-in-the-eu" tabindex="-1" class="icon-faq" hidden="true" data-rlta-element="panel" data-rlta-state="closed" data-rlta-color="false"><div data-rlta-element="panel-content"> <span style="font-size: 1rem;"></span></p><p>Yes, ESG certification is a significant advantage in meeting the EU's import requirements, facilitating smoother customs clearance.</p></div></div><div id="rlta-3-can-esg-certification-be-used-in-markets-outside-the-eu" role="button" aria-controls="rlta-panel-3-can-esg-certification-be-used-in-markets-outside-the-eu" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" class="icon-faq" data-rlta-alias="3-can-esg-certification-be-used-in-markets-outside-the-eu" data-rlta-element="button" data-rlta-state="closed"><div data-rlta-element="heading"> 3. Can ESG certification be used in markets outside the EU?</div></div><div id="rlta-panel-3-can-esg-certification-be-used-in-markets-outside-the-eu" aria-labelledby="rlta-3-can-esg-certification-be-used-in-markets-outside-the-eu" tabindex="-1" class="icon-faq" hidden="true" data-rlta-element="panel" data-rlta-state="closed" data-rlta-color="false"><div data-rlta-element="panel-content"><p>Yes. ESG Registered D&amp;B certification is globally recognized and applicable to many international markets.</p></div></div><div id="rlta-4-what-are-the-basic-requirements-to-obtain-esg-certification" role="button" aria-controls="rlta-panel-4-what-are-the-basic-requirements-to-obtain-esg-certification" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" class="icon-faq" data-rlta-alias="4-what-are-the-basic-requirements-to-obtain-esg-certification" data-rlta-element="button" data-rlta-state="closed"><div data-rlta-element="heading"> 4. What are the basic requirements to obtain ESG certification?</div></div><div id="rlta-panel-4-what-are-the-basic-requirements-to-obtain-esg-certification" aria-labelledby="rlta-4-what-are-the-basic-requirements-to-obtain-esg-certification" tabindex="-1" class="icon-faq" hidden="true" data-rlta-element="panel" data-rlta-state="closed" data-rlta-color="false"><div data-rlta-element="panel-content"><p>Businesses must meet the following standards:</p><ul> <li>Environmental: Minimize emissions, manage waste effectively.</li> <li>Social: Ensure proper labor conditions and contribute to community development.</li> <li>Governance: Maintain transparency and implement anti-corruption measures.</li> </ul> </div> </div><div id="rlta-5-what-eu-esg-regulations-should-businesses-be-aware-of" role="button" aria-controls="rlta-panel-5-what-eu-esg-regulations-should-businesses-be-aware-of" aria-expanded="false" tabindex="0" class="icon-faq" data-rlta-alias="5-what-eu-esg-regulations-should-businesses-be-aware-of" data-rlta-element="button" data-rlta-state="closed"><div data-rlta-element="heading"> 5. What EU ESG regulations should businesses be aware of?</div></div><div id="rlta-panel-5-what-eu-esg-regulations-should-businesses-be-aware-of" aria-labelledby="rlta-5-what-eu-esg-regulations-should-businesses-be-aware-of" tabindex="-1" class="icon-faq" hidden="true" data-rlta-element="panel" data-rlta-state="closed" data-rlta-color="false"><div data-rlta-element="panel-content"><ul> <li>Corporate Sustainability Reporting Directive (CSRD):Â Requires l